To get started:

(Mac OSX) sudo brew install libyaml
(Ubuntu) sudo apt-get install libyaml libyaml-dev

cd setup
./bootstrap.sh

You should see "Come get it" at the end

source env/bin/activate

Open a python shell and hack away:

from classifier import *
classifier = PartisanTweetClassifier()
classifier.fetch_twitter()
# Some output...
classifier.train()
classifier.accuracy()
classifier.salient_features()
